1
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,030
[The Princess Royal]

2
00:01:26,030 --> 00:01:28,950
[Adapted from Mo Shu Bai's novel,
The Princess Royal on jjwxc.net]

3
00:01:28,950 --> 00:01:30,020
[This is a work of fiction.]

4
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 14]

5
00:01:40,780 --> 00:01:41,940
No need to take the whole kit

6
00:01:41,940 --> 00:01:43,060
for a small cut.

7
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:44,620
Your Highness,

8
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:45,820
I have an idea.

9
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:47,140
It might be very blunt,

10
00:01:47,140 --> 00:01:48,460
but it's just a suggestion.

11
00:01:48,460 --> 00:01:49,460
You can keep it to yourself
if it's blunt.

12
00:01:49,460 --> 00:01:50,540
No, I should say it out loud.

13
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:52,620
What about Su Rongqing

14
00:01:52,620 --> 00:01:53,900
as a potential candidate?

15
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:03,300
Look at me. Why would I bring him up?

16
00:02:03,300 --> 00:02:04,620
Mr. Pei is here.

17
00:02:04,740 --> 00:02:07,300
You're the Prince Consort, after all.

18
00:02:08,420 --> 00:02:09,180
You can continue.

19
00:02:09,180 --> 00:02:10,580
Mr. Pei is very generous.

20
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:11,220
Right?

21
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:12,460
Yes.

22
00:02:12,900 --> 00:02:15,060
Feel free to speak your mind,
Miss Shangguan.

23
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:17,940
I observed Mr. Su's reaction today,

24
00:02:17,940 --> 00:02:20,380
and I believe he has
some feelings for you, Your Highness.

25
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:22,860
If we can persuade him
to join the Inspectorate Office,

26
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,900
it will be easier

27
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:24,980
for us to make moves in the future.

28
00:02:27,140 --> 00:02:28,620
What do you mean, Miss Shangguan?

29
00:02:31,380 --> 00:02:32,380
See?

30
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,740
I offended Mr. Pei here.

31
00:02:38,940 --> 00:02:40,260
It's fine. Please continue.

32
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:42,700
Feelings can be developed.

33
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:43,980
If you don't mind, Your Highness,

34
00:02:44,140 --> 00:02:45,180
I can arrange it for you.

35
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:46,140
Arrange what?

36
00:02:47,300 --> 00:02:48,060
Her Highness's marriage

37
00:02:48,060 --> 00:02:49,940
shouldn't be mixed together
with those things.

38
00:02:52,460 --> 00:02:53,260
Furthermore,

39
00:02:53,460 --> 00:02:54,420
my marriage with Her Highness

40
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:55,700
is a scheme.

41
00:02:55,940 --> 00:02:57,180
If we had a second chance,

42
00:02:57,340 --> 00:02:59,420
shouldn't we avoid
making the same mistake?

43
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,540
Don't you agree, Your Highness?

44
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:08,100
♪May time itself ask me♪

45
00:03:08,100 --> 00:03:08,860
Mr. Pei,

46
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,100
I beg to differ.

47
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,940
It's not right to sacrifice love

48
00:03:12,940 --> 00:03:14,260
for power, of course.

49
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:17,580
But if Her Highness fancies him,

50
00:03:17,620 --> 00:03:20,620
isn't that making use of an opportunity
to help them get together?

51
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:22,780
We're both Her Highness's friends.

52
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:24,140
As her besties,

53
00:03:24,140 --> 00:03:25,900
we must act in her best interest.

54
00:03:27,180 --> 00:03:30,540
Unless you have another motive, Mr. Pei.

55
00:03:30,540 --> 00:03:32,460
♪I thought capturing your heart
meant forever♪

56
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:34,260
♪Yet, it turned out to be
as fleeting as autumn♪

57
00:03:34,260 --> 00:03:35,620
No, I do not have any.

58
00:03:36,820 --> 00:03:40,540
I just don't know
if you have a feeling for him.

59
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:46,660
♪I'd follow you with no hesitation♪

60
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:51,300
♪Ready to surrender everything
to this sensation♪

61
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,100
Well,

62
00:03:52,100 --> 00:03:53,020
I have another appointment,

63
00:03:53,020 --> 00:03:54,020
so I must take my leave now.

64
00:03:54,140 --> 00:03:56,180
Your Highness, if you're interested,

65
00:03:56,180 --> 00:03:57,380
you can just send me a message.

66
00:03:57,540 --> 00:03:58,580
I'll arrange it for you.

67
00:03:59,220 --> 00:04:00,220
I'll think about it.

68
00:04:00,340 --> 00:04:01,180
I'm leaving.

69
00:04:01,180 --> 00:04:03,980
♪Grant me a ceaseless passion♪

70
00:04:03,980 --> 00:04:09,500
♪Let me face trials and tribulations
with you♪

71
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,980
♪Let us bathe in love's endless grace♪

72
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:14,740
What do you think of her suggestion?

73
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:18,380
I think

74
00:04:18,740 --> 00:04:19,500
that she makes sense.

75
00:04:19,740 --> 00:04:20,860
Nothing

76
00:04:21,060 --> 00:04:23,140
is set in stone yet,

77
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,980
so we might as well play along.

78
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:26,580
It's impractical
to visit the Ministry of Justice

79
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,100
all the time to make a scene.

80
00:04:28,300 --> 00:04:30,340
We need an intermediary.

81
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:33,380
I should talk to him.

82
00:04:35,700 --> 00:04:37,860
I can negotiate with him on your behalf.

83
00:04:39,020 --> 00:04:40,260
If you don't want

84
00:04:40,380 --> 00:04:42,300
to visit the Ministry of Justice,

85
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:44,020
we can seek an alternative.

86
00:04:44,580 --> 00:04:45,700
I'm willing to help.

87
00:04:45,700 --> 00:04:47,260
Why do you keep stopping me

88
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:48,460
from seeing him?

89
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,780
Didn't you tell me

90
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,660
to give him a chance?

91
00:05:00,820 --> 00:05:01,540
Li Rong.

92
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:05,100
We got married
because we wanted to gain power.

93
00:05:05,940 --> 00:05:07,420
Even if we're getting a divorce,

94
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:09,740
I still hope you'll find

95
00:05:09,740 --> 00:05:11,500
a man you like,

96
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:12,220
not a random person.

97
00:05:14,300 --> 00:05:14,980
If you're

98
00:05:15,220 --> 00:05:17,540
approaching Su Rongqing for power,

99
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:19,980
then there will be no difference
from the situation we are in now.

100
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,300
Of course, there's a difference.

101
00:05:21,620 --> 00:05:23,540
I'm not saying I'll be with him now.

102
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:25,780
I'll wait until I know
that I'm in love with him.

103
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:26,940
Why don't you find out the answer now?

104
00:05:26,940 --> 00:05:28,020
How?

105
00:05:37,660 --> 00:05:39,060
What's wrong with you today?

106
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:43,100
You are never this temperamental.

107
00:05:50,140 --> 00:05:51,260
Don't they say the older you get,

108
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:53,460
the more childish you become?

109
00:05:54,580 --> 00:05:56,580
You cut yourself today

110
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:57,700
because of a recording officer.

111
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,740
That is inappropriate of you.

112
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:01,420
Don't do this again.

113
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:04,500
I know.

114
00:06:07,300 --> 00:06:10,100
While people do say
that I carry a noble body,

115
00:06:10,820 --> 00:06:11,980
I'm still a human.

116
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:13,860
You don't have to patch me up
like this for a small cut.

117
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:15,460
This is ridiculous.

118
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:16,660
Not at all.

119
00:06:17,700 --> 00:06:19,620
You have to keep yourself safe.

120
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:27,020
What are you implying?

121
00:06:32,900 --> 00:06:34,100
Nothing.

122
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:35,700
I'm just worried that Su Rongqing

123
00:06:36,020 --> 00:06:37,020
might complain about me

124
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,780
in the court tomorrow.

125
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:44,460
Aren't you two sworn brothers
or something?

126
00:06:45,460 --> 00:06:46,380
Enough.

127
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:47,620
Don't worry.

128
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:48,780
Father

129
00:06:48,780 --> 00:06:50,580
will only punish you lightly
and deduct your salary.

130
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:52,060
You know what?

131
00:06:52,420 --> 00:06:53,820
I'll pay you back

132
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:55,420
what my father will take from you.

133
00:06:57,460 --> 00:06:58,580
If that's still not enough,

134
00:06:59,700 --> 00:07:01,420
once I really establish a relationship
with Su Rongqing,

135
00:07:01,620 --> 00:07:02,860
I'll ask him to pay you back tenfold.

136
00:07:08,860 --> 00:07:12,220
Should I thank you then?

137
00:07:12,380 --> 00:07:13,020
No need.

138
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,220
Don't worry.

139
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:16,580
Such a trivial matter
will not bother me at all.

140
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:18,140
I should go.

141
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:19,060
Where are you going?

142
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:22,660
Just do what you're supposed to do.

143
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:25,380
I'll ask Chuan to communicate
with your superior tomorrow

144
00:07:25,420 --> 00:07:26,660
so that he won't give you extra work.

145
00:07:27,180 --> 00:07:27,980
I won't take no for an answer.

146
00:07:38,260 --> 00:07:39,020
All right.

147
00:07:39,340 --> 00:07:40,260
Don't stay out too late.

148
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:41,420
Rest early.

149
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:42,500
I will.

150
00:08:00,140 --> 00:08:01,860
The case files contain three parts.

151
00:08:01,900 --> 00:08:02,900
The first one contains

152
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:05,020
the background of the Qin Family's case.

153
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:07,900
The second one contains
the investigation methods

154
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:10,380
and the reports issued and approved
by the officers involved.

155
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:12,700
The third one contains

156
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:16,380
the transcripts of all the witnesses's
testimonies and the evidence.

157
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:18,620
The testimonies and the evidence
are kept elsewhere.

158
00:08:18,820 --> 00:08:20,460
We won't have access to them
for the moment.

159
00:08:21,180 --> 00:08:21,980
However,

160
00:08:22,220 --> 00:08:23,660
there's a breakthrough.

161
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:25,060
And that is this case is found

162
00:08:25,780 --> 00:08:27,300
by Wen Ping, an investigating censor

163
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:29,900
from the Censorate.

164
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:32,300
Wen Ping received a report letter

165
00:08:32,580 --> 00:08:34,860
claiming that when the Great Xia
and the enemies went to war,

166
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:36,740
the Qin Family
was defending Huangping County.

167
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,420
Three thousand soldiers stayed to defend

168
00:08:38,540 --> 00:08:40,020
while three thousand enemies
came to invade.

169
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:43,780
[Military Record]
Yang Ye later asked the Qin Family

170
00:08:44,060 --> 00:08:45,060
to feign surrender and flee the city.

171
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:47,140
After Wen Ping received the letter,

172
00:08:47,220 --> 00:08:48,100
he retrieved

173
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:50,180
the official record of the battle
from the Ministry of War.

174
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:52,020
Three thousand soldiers
defended the city.

175
00:08:52,020 --> 00:08:52,900
Three thousand enemies came invading.

176
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:54,180
The city was then abandoned.

177
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:54,860
Someone!

178
00:08:55,020 --> 00:08:56,060
By right,

179
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:58,180
the invaders can only claim the city
if they outnumber

180
00:08:58,180 --> 00:08:59,100
the defenders.

181
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,140
When both factions are of equal power,

182
00:09:01,460 --> 00:09:02,700
this shouldn't be the outcome.

183
00:09:03,620 --> 00:09:04,380
Luo Juan.

184
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,260
Confess now.

185
00:09:06,620 --> 00:09:09,500
What truly happened in the battle
occurred in Huangping County?

186
00:09:10,620 --> 00:09:11,260
Come clean!

187
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:14,780
Otherwise, you'll suffer more.

188
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:15,860
Back then...

189
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,380
the Qin Family could win.

190
00:09:21,660 --> 00:09:23,620
Or at least, they wouldn't lose.

191
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:26,060
They abandoned the city.

192
00:09:28,420 --> 00:09:29,100
Someone.

193
00:09:29,740 --> 00:09:31,620
Ask the Ministry of War to assist us

194
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:34,460
in retrieving the military record
of the battle

195
00:09:34,500 --> 00:09:35,780
so we can verify the situation.

196
00:09:36,300 --> 00:09:37,060
Sirs,

197
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:39,820
this is the conclusion I've arrived at.

198
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,820
All evidence indicates
that the Qin Family

199
00:09:42,100 --> 00:09:44,100
colluded with the enemies,
and betrayed the nation.

200
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,300
Then

201
00:09:49,420 --> 00:09:50,460
seize the Qin's Mansion

202
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:51,860
and detain all personnel
according to the law.

203
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:52,620
Yes, sir.

204
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:55,140
The Qin Family is found guilty
of embezzling military funds,

205
00:09:55,140 --> 00:09:56,500
colluding with enemies
and committing treason

206
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:57,780
with the Yang Family.
The evidence is clear.

207
00:09:58,140 --> 00:10:00,620
Arrest
the entire Qin Family immediately.

208
00:10:02,780 --> 00:10:03,380
Stop.

209
00:10:08,140 --> 00:10:08,860
Qin Lang.

210
00:10:09,380 --> 00:10:10,740
The evidence is clear.

211
00:10:11,020 --> 00:10:11,900
Will you plead guilty or not?

212
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:14,460
Continue.

213
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:20,260
Stop.

214
00:10:25,660 --> 00:10:26,540
Will you plead guilty or not?

215
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,220
Yes.

216
00:10:32,020 --> 00:10:33,660
They've put a lot of effort into it
and tried to take the lives

217
00:10:33,780 --> 00:10:36,140
of the entire Qin Family
with a mere one thousand taels of gold.

218
00:10:36,540 --> 00:10:38,140
What a low price.

219
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:42,020
There are three entry points.

220
00:10:43,900 --> 00:10:44,780
First,

221
00:10:45,460 --> 00:10:47,260
find out the one who wrote the letter.

222
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:49,620
Then, it's Luo Juan.

223
00:10:50,260 --> 00:10:51,980
Luo Juan must have
given a false testimony.

224
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,980
We need to find out more people

225
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:55,740
who participated in the battle.

226
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:57,860
Then, it's Yang Ye's letter.

227
00:10:58,380 --> 00:11:00,340
We need to see it
to verify its veracity.

228
00:11:00,780 --> 00:11:02,500
Lastly, that 1,000 taels of gold.

229
00:11:03,340 --> 00:11:05,340
We need to locate those
who raided the Qin's Mansion.

230
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:06,900
Only they know

231
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:08,660
how the money got inside.

232
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:11,500
Tomorrow, I'll ask Xun Chuan

233
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:13,140
to go to Luo Juan and the veterans
who fought in the battle.

234
00:11:14,260 --> 00:11:18,020
As for Yang Ye's letter and those
who raided the Qin's Mansion...

235
00:11:20,620 --> 00:11:23,500
it'd be best if Su Rongqing
could help us with them.

236
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:26,740
Is she going
to go to Su Rongqing again?

237
00:11:26,860 --> 00:11:27,740
But

238
00:11:28,140 --> 00:11:29,980
what if Su Rongqing
refuses to cooperate?

239
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:35,540
I believe

240
00:11:35,620 --> 00:11:37,660
we should avoid
having too much interaction with him.

241
00:11:37,980 --> 00:11:40,900
After all, we don't know
if he's an ally or an enemy.

242
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:47,260
Then

243
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:50,100
We'll have to find out if we can
find another ally

244
00:11:50,100 --> 00:11:50,860
in the Ministry of Justice.

245
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:54,220
Or, we take the normal procedures.

246
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:57,100
I'll give those who don't show us
the evidence a hard time

247
00:11:57,340 --> 00:11:59,140
until they find us the evidence.

248
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:02,260
This is a much better option
than going to Su Rongqing.

249
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:05,740
You don't like him, do you?

250
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:07,740
It's not like that.

251
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,020
It's also...

252
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:13,140
Young Master?

253
00:12:13,780 --> 00:12:14,540
Your Highness?

254
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:22,020
Never mind that.

255
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:24,860
Tell Miss Shangguan

256
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:27,340
that she can arrange it for me
as she wants

257
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:28,340
as soon as possible.

258
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:29,300
Ask Xun Chuan

259
00:12:29,700 --> 00:12:30,980
to gather 12 elite ones

260
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:32,460
to be Her Highness's guards.

261
00:12:33,300 --> 00:12:33,900
Yes, sir.

262
00:12:34,470 --> 00:12:36,250
[Censorate]

263
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:38,580
Stop.

264
00:12:40,340 --> 00:12:41,580
Who are you?

265
00:12:44,540 --> 00:12:45,580
Mr. Wen.

266
00:12:45,740 --> 00:12:47,660
I am Pei Wenxuan,
with Wujin as my courtesy name,

267
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:49,340
a palace attendant in the Censorate.

268
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:50,580
Oh?

269
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:53,660
You're from the Censorate?

270
00:12:55,380 --> 00:12:57,060
Why didn't I see you

271
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:59,580
when I did the roll call today?

272
00:12:59,700 --> 00:13:00,580
I am terribly sorry.

273
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:02,100
I was accompanying Princess Pingyue...

274
00:13:02,100 --> 00:13:03,860
Are you the prince consort

275
00:13:04,060 --> 00:13:05,900
