00:26:36,060 --> 00:26:37,300
Yes, I have to get ready.

562
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:40,100
Ya finally got us the opportunity.

563
00:26:40,220 --> 00:26:41,740
I can't let her down.

564
00:26:42,420 --> 00:26:43,380
I'll get changed

565
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:44,340
and dress up.

566
00:26:48,580 --> 00:26:49,540
Must you go?

567
00:26:55,540 --> 00:26:56,700
I mean

568
00:26:57,740 --> 00:26:59,020
the Qin Family's case files...

569
00:26:59,020 --> 00:26:59,820
I've read them.

570
00:27:03,460 --> 00:27:04,420
Then Luo Juan

571
00:27:04,820 --> 00:27:06,900
and the people involved in the battle
occurred in Huangping County...

572
00:27:06,900 --> 00:27:07,980
Xun Chuan is investigating that.

573
00:27:10,180 --> 00:27:11,860
When I meet Su Rongqing later,

574
00:27:12,140 --> 00:27:14,100
we'll see what we can learn from him.

575
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:15,860
Do you have other concerns?

576
00:27:17,020 --> 00:27:17,740
No.

577
00:27:20,220 --> 00:27:22,220
Don't worry. I'll come home early.

578
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:23,900
You have to be careful too.

579
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:26,180
Many people in the court
are keeping an eye on you.

580
00:27:27,420 --> 00:27:28,180
Don't worry.

581
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:29,580
I will be cautious.

582
00:27:30,940 --> 00:27:33,340
May your plan go smoothly,

583
00:27:33,660 --> 00:27:34,500
Your Highness.

584
00:27:38,580 --> 00:27:39,900
I'll go back now. Enjoy the food.

585
00:27:50,140 --> 00:27:50,660
Mr. Pei.

586
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,580
Young... Young Master!

587
00:27:54,980 --> 00:27:55,820
What are you doing here?

588
00:27:58,780 --> 00:27:59,540
Young Master,

589
00:27:59,780 --> 00:28:00,740
the Pei family sent a message

590
00:28:00,740 --> 00:28:02,500
claiming that your mother was sick.
They want you to go back.

591
00:28:02,620 --> 00:28:03,660
Mother is sick?

592
00:28:04,460 --> 00:28:05,860
Why wasn't I informed?

593
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:06,980
Right.

594
00:28:07,180 --> 00:28:08,380
You asked me to keep a close watch

595
00:28:08,380 --> 00:28:09,620
and I did.

596
00:28:09,620 --> 00:28:11,340
But there was no news whatsoever.

597
00:28:11,580 --> 00:28:12,660
The messenger said

598
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:14,100
that your mother intentionally
concealed her illness

599
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:15,220
so as not to burden you.

600
00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:16,220
An hour ago,

601
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,500
she fainted.

602
00:28:18,220 --> 00:28:19,780
They couldn't get a physician in.

603
00:28:21,780 --> 00:28:24,100
I suspect someone in the family
didn't want to get her any help.

604
00:28:24,140 --> 00:28:24,820
Do you see it?

605
00:28:25,780 --> 00:28:26,420
Let's go.

606
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:30,180
Head to Mingyue Restaurant.
Once Her Highness is done,

607
00:28:30,420 --> 00:28:31,620
ask her to come to the Pei's Mansion
to pick me up.

608
00:28:38,140 --> 00:28:39,060
I... I...

609
00:28:39,420 --> 00:28:40,740
Ask her to bring more men with her.

610
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:42,940
Okay.

611
00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:43,500
Go now.

612
00:28:43,700 --> 00:28:44,300
Wait.

613
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:46,340
Wait for her by the entrance.

614
00:28:46,340 --> 00:28:47,900
Do not disturb Her Highness.
Do you hear me?

615
00:28:49,740 --> 00:28:50,460
Go now.

616
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:51,700
Yes.

617
00:28:55,820 --> 00:28:57,500
Ronghua, you mean

618
00:28:58,100 --> 00:29:00,860
Her Highness asked you
to invite me to a private meeting?

619
00:29:01,780 --> 00:29:02,820
To be precise,

620
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:05,100
she asked Shangguan Ya
to make the request.

621
00:29:06,820 --> 00:29:07,860
And

622
00:29:08,500 --> 00:29:10,140
Pei Wenxuan is aware of this?

623
00:29:11,780 --> 00:29:12,700
It seems like it.

624
00:29:16,140 --> 00:29:17,180
Everyone alleges

625
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:20,060
that Princess Pingyue
betrothed Pei Wenxuan

626
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:22,300
out of convenience.

627
00:29:22,860 --> 00:29:23,900
It seems like

628
00:29:24,980 --> 00:29:25,980
that is the truth.

629
00:29:28,140 --> 00:29:29,060
I think

630
00:29:29,580 --> 00:29:31,660
you can meet Her Highness.

631
00:29:32,980 --> 00:29:33,580
All right.

632
00:29:36,780 --> 00:29:39,300
Please tell Her Highness

633
00:29:39,740 --> 00:29:40,620
that I'll be there.

634
00:29:46,540 --> 00:29:47,540
What are you doing here?

635
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:50,220
I am here to escort you.

636
00:29:53,740 --> 00:29:56,140
You just don't want to be left out.

637
00:29:58,220 --> 00:29:58,860
What do you think?

638
00:29:59,180 --> 00:29:59,860
Do I look good?

639
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:02,580
Yes,

640
00:30:02,860 --> 00:30:04,460
just a bit too formal.

641
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:07,100
It shows a sense of oppression.

642
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,540
It seems like

643
00:30:08,540 --> 00:30:11,820
you are condescending.

644
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:13,420
For this meeting,

645
00:30:13,420 --> 00:30:14,540
it's best to present yourself

646
00:30:14,540 --> 00:30:16,980
as equals.

647
00:30:20,140 --> 00:30:21,660
But I am a princess.

648
00:30:22,300 --> 00:30:25,780
No matter how I dress,
I can't hide my temperament.

649
00:30:26,140 --> 00:30:26,940
Your Highness,

650
00:30:27,100 --> 00:30:29,340
I may give you some advice.

651
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:31,620
Let's start with your way of speaking.

652
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:34,300
When you talk to a man,

653
00:30:34,620 --> 00:30:37,780
avoid speaking in a bossy manner.

654
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:39,620
Do not move.

655
00:30:39,780 --> 00:30:40,540
That's it.

656
00:30:41,100 --> 00:30:43,020
You always lift your chin
when you speak.

657
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:44,500
That's what a princess does.

658
00:30:45,220 --> 00:30:46,860
But for ordinary women,

659
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:48,860
we lower our heads

660
00:30:48,900 --> 00:30:49,700
and brows.

661
00:30:49,820 --> 00:30:50,740
And when we speak,

662
00:30:50,860 --> 00:30:52,460
- we do this.
- We do this.

663
00:30:56,700 --> 00:30:57,700
I know,

664
00:30:58,060 --> 00:30:59,340
but that's not me.

665
00:30:59,540 --> 00:31:00,260
Your Highness...

666
00:31:01,060 --> 00:31:01,860
Enough.

667
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,260
Your Highness.

668
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:05,900
Your Highness.

669
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:07,860
Rongqing,

670
00:31:09,180 --> 00:31:10,300
I can't walk further.

671
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,300
You've been browsing for an hour,

672
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:13,500
and you still can't make up your mind.

673
00:31:16,020 --> 00:31:17,500
It's rare for Her Highness
to invite me for a meal.

674
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:20,100
I must pick a fitting gift
for the occasion.

675
00:31:21,820 --> 00:31:22,780
I have an idea.

676
00:31:23,260 --> 00:31:24,220
What about food?

677
00:31:24,580 --> 00:31:26,980
The lamb stew
from Hongqing Restaurant is good.

678
00:31:27,140 --> 00:31:28,420
It comes with a fancy package too.

679
00:31:29,820 --> 00:31:30,580
No.

680
00:31:30,580 --> 00:31:32,020
Food is too common.

681
00:31:32,340 --> 00:31:33,220
It lacks sincerity.

682
00:31:38,060 --> 00:31:38,740
Rongqing,

683
00:31:39,780 --> 00:31:41,020
what about an accessory?

684
00:31:41,780 --> 00:31:43,260
You can't go wrong with a hairpin.

685
00:31:44,260 --> 00:31:45,060
An accessory?

686
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:47,180
No.

687
00:31:48,300 --> 00:31:50,100
Her Highness will refuse
an expensive gift.

688
00:31:50,460 --> 00:31:51,940
Besides, it is inappropriate for me

689
00:31:52,820 --> 00:31:53,700
to give her accessories
with my current identity.

690
00:31:55,220 --> 00:31:56,140
Sirs!

691
00:31:56,380 --> 00:31:57,500
Come take a look.

692
00:31:57,660 --> 00:31:59,900
Fresh flowers I plucked this morning.

693
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:00,980
Take a look.

694
00:32:02,900 --> 00:32:04,220
Pick anything you like.

695
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:07,020
Rongqing,

696
00:32:07,780 --> 00:32:09,100
I remember you said

697
00:32:09,100 --> 00:32:10,500
that Her Highness
loved peonies the most.

698
00:32:12,780 --> 00:32:14,300
For a lady of such mesmerizing beauty,

699
00:32:14,420 --> 00:32:15,700
only a peony can match her charm.

700
00:32:16,140 --> 00:32:16,780
All right.

701
00:32:17,060 --> 00:32:17,740
I'll take this one.

702
00:32:17,980 --> 00:32:18,660
Sure.

703
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:32,100
Greetings, Grandfather.

704
00:32:33,420 --> 00:32:34,380
Greetings, Mother.

705
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:36,380
Greetings to all.

706
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:53,460
I was told Mother fell ill,

707
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:54,740
so I rushed back.

708
00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:57,340
It seems like

709
00:32:57,700 --> 00:32:59,900
you are fine, Mother.

710
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:02,100
I...

711
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:06,420
I summoned you here.

712
00:33:06,980 --> 00:33:08,460
I knew you wouldn't heed my call,

713
00:33:09,540 --> 00:33:11,420
so I asked your mother
to bring you here.

714
00:33:11,980 --> 00:33:13,060
Why would you say that, Grandfather?

715
00:33:13,380 --> 00:33:14,700
If the elderly in the family needs me,

716
00:33:14,900 --> 00:33:16,260
I wouldn't dare not to come back.

717
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:20,100
However,
lying about my mother falling sick

718
00:33:20,660 --> 00:33:22,620
has made me terribly worried.

719
00:33:23,420 --> 00:33:25,500
If you were truly
concerned about this family,

720
00:33:26,940 --> 00:33:28,660
you wouldn't have urged Her Highness

721
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:30,860
to do those obstructive things.

722
00:33:32,420 --> 00:33:33,700
I do not understand,

723
00:33:34,140 --> 00:33:35,460
Second Uncle.

724
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:37,340
You asked Her Highness to establish

725
00:33:37,620 --> 00:33:39,060
the Inspectorate Office, didn't you?

726
00:33:41,980 --> 00:33:42,900
I see it now.

727
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:46,340
You brought everyone here
for this matter.

728
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:48,820
Second Uncle, you may direct

729
00:33:49,340 --> 00:33:50,860
your dissatisfaction to Her Highness.

730
00:33:52,700 --> 00:33:53,500
Wenxuan,

731
00:33:54,220 --> 00:33:55,740
you are the Prince Consort.

732
00:33:55,780 --> 00:33:57,860
She may be reckless

733
00:33:57,940 --> 00:33:59,380
but you cannot afford that.

734
00:33:59,740 --> 00:34:02,940
Other families have come
and questioned us.

735
00:34:03,300 --> 00:34:05,860
In the past, she couldn't
care less about the state affairs.

736
00:34:06,100 --> 00:34:09,420
After she betrothed you,
she meddled in everyone's affairs.

737
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:11,140
This must have something
to do with you.

738
00:34:12,700 --> 00:34:14,260
Even if we could believe you,

739
00:34:14,420 --> 00:34:16,060
no one from the outside would.

740
00:34:16,260 --> 00:34:17,100
So,

741
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:20,020
what do you want me to do?

742
00:34:30,260 --> 00:34:31,060
Wenxuan.

743
00:34:32,100 --> 00:34:34,500
Listen to us.

744
00:34:35,580 --> 00:34:38,580
Talk to Her Highness and tell her

745
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:42,100
not to be enemies
with the noble families.

746
00:34:42,620 --> 00:34:44,580
If our family is implicated,

747
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:47,740
Her Highness will remain untouched,

748
00:34:48,420 --> 00:34:49,500
but our family will...

749
00:34:49,500 --> 00:34:50,460
Our family will what?

750
00:34:52,500 --> 00:34:53,260
Mother,

751
00:34:54,020 --> 00:34:55,780
how could you believe
whatever they told you?

752
00:34:55,780 --> 00:34:56,380
I...

753
00:35:00,660 --> 00:35:01,860
What do you want me to do?

754
00:35:02,780 --> 00:35:03,660
Go back

755
00:35:04,380 --> 00:35:07,100
and tell Her Highness
to stay out of the affairs.

756
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:10,780
Just...

757
00:35:11,220 --> 00:35:11,900
Just...

758
00:35:12,700 --> 00:35:15,580
Just forget about the Qin Family's case.

759
00:35:18,780 --> 00:35:21,540
So, it's all about
the Qin Family's case, isn't it?

760
00:35:22,380 --> 00:35:23,020
I see.

761
00:35:23,740 --> 00:35:24,620
Anything else?

762
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:27,180
You...

763
00:35:30,620 --> 00:35:31,740
What is

764
00:35:32,660 --> 00:35:34,540
that attitude?

765
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:37,460
Do you have no respect for me?

766
00:35:37,460 --> 00:35:38,300
I do.

767
00:35:40,140 --> 00:35:40,980
But do you?

768
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:42,180
I...

769
00:35:42,180 --> 00:35:44,020
My sister-in-law,

770
00:35:44,020 --> 00:35:45,580
look at your child.

771
00:35:45,860 --> 00:35:48,100
You must discipline him.

772
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:50,620
He... He...

773
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:55,180
How dare you defy us?

774
00:35:56,460 --> 00:35:58,660
Punish him. Punish him.

775
00:35:58,780 --> 00:35:59,260
Someone!

776
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:00,020
Punish me?

777
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:01,620
Mother.

778
00:36:02,500 --> 00:36:03,740
Was it that they told you
that by punishing me,

779
00:36:04,060 --> 00:36:06,500
the other noble families
would be appeased,

780
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:08,300
and that Her Highness would back off?

781
00:36:12,380 --> 00:36:14,900
In the future, if I ever
urge Her Highness to do anything,

782
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:16,260
you'll punish me again,

783
00:36:16,940 --> 00:36:18,180
until I cease.

784
00:36:19,100 --> 00:36:19,740
Is that so?

785
00:36:27,740 --> 00:36:30,500
I knew this would happen.

786
00:36:31,700 --> 00:36:32,860
I just didn't expect you...

787
00:36:35,460 --> 00:36:37,100
to follow through
with their plan, Mother.

788
00:36:40,020 --> 00:36:41,100
Don't just stand there.

789
00:36:42,580 --> 00:36:43,380
Get him

790
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:44,700
and punish him.

791
00:37:20,100 --> 00:37:21,660
Wenxuan.

792
00:37:22,980 --> 00:37:23,580
I...

793
00:37:24,500 --> 00:37:25,180
I...

794
00:37:25,460 --> 00:37:27,260
I know you cannot bear
to see this scene.

795
00:37:27,660 --> 00:37:28,580
You may turn around.

796
00:37:31,260 --> 00:37:32,140
Stop!

797
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:36,100
My child...

798
00:37:37,540 --> 00:37:39,500
just admit that you are wrong.

799
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:43,860
I am not wrong.

800
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:44,620
Not wrong?

801
00:37:45,140 --> 00:37:45,900
Come on, Father.

802
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:47,860
Hit him until he admits that he's wrong.

803
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:48,660
Continue.

804
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:52,740
Her Highness was right downstairs,

805
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:54,620
but she had to leave
because something came up.

806
00:37:54,700 --> 00:37:56,100
Go and tell Mr. Su

807
00:37:56,100 --> 00:37:58,100
so that he won't wait in vain
and get mad at Her Highness.

808
00:37:58,420 --> 00:37:59,700
Quickly.

809
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:03,180
My poor brother.

810
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,700
No one has ever

811
00:38:04,740 --> 00:38:06,460
taken him for a fool like this.

812
00:38:07,500 --> 00:38:08,140
Perhaps

813
00:38:08,580 --> 00:38:10,020
I should tell him the truth.

814
00:38:10,020 --> 00:38:10,540
Wait.

815
00:38:12,540 --> 00:38:14,060
I'll dine with you three times.

816
00:38:14,700 --> 00:38:15,580
You can pick the restaurant.

817
00:38:16,900 --> 00:38:17,500
Deal.

818
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,660
Young Master told me
not to disturb you, Your Highness.

819
00:38:22,660 --> 00:38:23,420
Where were you doing?

820
00:38:23,420 --> 00:38:24,700
I was waiting for you.

821
00:38:24,700 --> 00:38:25,900
Young Master told me
to tell you after the meal.

822
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:26,740
Enough.

823
00:38:28,220 --> 00:38:29,180
Your Highness.

824
00:38:30,260 --> 00:38:31,140
They won't let us in.

825
00:38:33,100 --> 00:38:33,700
Move aside.

826
00:38:37,620 --> 00:38:38,380
Barge in.

827
00:38:38,580 --> 00:38:39,180
Let's go.

828
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:52,940
Master!

829
00:38:53,220 --> 00:38:54,020
Bad news.

830
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:55,100
Her Highness barged in.

831
00:39:09,140 --> 00:39:09,860
Xun Chuan.

832
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:21,780
Why is the Prince Consort kneeling?

833
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:23,380
Help him up.

834
00:39:23,460 --> 00:39:24,100
Yes.

835
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,140
Your Highness.

836
00:39:27,140 --> 00:39:28,980
- Your Highness.
- Your Highness.

837
00:39:58,300 --> 00:40:00,220
I have some harsh words to say

838
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:02,380
in front of the ancestors

839
00:40:03,060 --> 00:40:04,100
of your family today.

840
00:40:04,740 --> 00:40:05,500
Your Highness,

841
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:07,580
perhaps you can keep...

842
00:40:26,740 --> 00:40:28,700
I was having a meal.

843
00:40:30,580 --> 00:40:33,620
And you tricked my consort
into serving a punishment here.

844
00:40:33,900 --> 00:40:35,620
May I remind you
that he is the Prince Consort

845
00:40:35,620 --> 00:40:36,740
and a member of the imperial family?

