00:40:41,580 --> 00:40:42,940
Who hit him?

849
00:40:43,140 --> 00:40:44,220
Who sanctioned the punishment?

850
00:40:44,620 --> 00:40:46,060
Come clean at once.

851
00:40:49,700 --> 00:40:50,540
Your Highness,

852
00:40:50,940 --> 00:40:52,500
I know you want

853
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:54,100
to protect your consort.

854
00:40:54,380 --> 00:40:57,460
