to Huajing from Luzhou,

883
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:11,740
promoting you into the higher echelon.

884
00:42:12,140 --> 00:42:13,780
He died not long ago,

885
00:42:14,540 --> 00:42:16,580
yet you're already bullying
his son and his wife.

886
00:42:19,420 --> 00:42:20,100
Your Highness,

887
00:42:20,500 --> 00:42:21,380
your criticism

888
00:42:22,540 --> 00:42:24,260
is unjustly harsh.

889
00:42:24,660 --> 00:42:25,300
Unjustly harsh?

890
00:42:28,460 --> 00:42:30,100
Pei Wenxuan was the top one
in the Royal Selection.

891
00:42:31,220 --> 00:42:32,260
He is more than capable

892
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:35,460
of occupying an important position.

893
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:37,380
If he hadn't betrothed me,

894
00:42:38,100 --> 00:42:38,780
he would've still been

895
00:42:38,780 --> 00:42:40,700
a lowly official
who's inferior to a prison guard.

896
00:42:41,860 --> 00:42:42,580
What did you do?

897
00:42:44,100 --> 00:42:45,740
You used the excuse
