898
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:47,100
must start from the ground

899
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:48,940
to silence his mother.

900
00:42:51,580 --> 00:42:52,380
When he was sick,

901
00:42:53,500 --> 00:42:55,140
you actively stopped him
from seeing a physician.

902
00:42:55,460 --> 00:42:56,860
When he needed money
to interact with other officials,

903
00:42:56,860 --> 00:42:58,100
you made his life more difficult.

904
00:42:58,700 --> 00:43:01,220
He works for the imperial court

905
00:43:01,300 --> 00:43:02,900
in hopes of escaping this predicament,

906
00:43:02,900 --> 00:43:04,260
yet you continue to impede him.

907
00:43:06,060 --> 00:43:07,220
He can turn a blind eye to you,

908
00:43:07,580 --> 00:43:08,860
but don't ever think I will do the same!

909
00:43:16,260 --> 00:43:19,580
I want to establish
the Inspectorate Office,

910
00:43:20,780 --> 00:43:22,100
and so does His Majesty.

911
00:43:23,300 --> 00:43:24,860
Even if you kill him today,

912
00:43:25,260 --> 00:43:27,100
His Majesty or I

913
00:43:28,540 --> 00:43:29,660
will not stop.

914
00:43:34,100 --> 00:43:35,380
Remember

915
00:43:36,220 --> 00:43:38,020
your root.

916
00:43:38,780 --> 00:43:40,140
Don't get too complacent

917
00:43:41,100 --> 00:43:42,420
in your lofty position.

918
00:43:43,100 --> 00:43:43,780
Your Highness,

919
00:43:44,220 --> 00:43:46,700
even though you are a princess,

920
00:43:47,180 --> 00:43:48,780
you are nonetheless a junior member
in this family.

921
00:43:49,140 --> 00:43:51,580
Should I inform His Majesty

922
00:43:52,100 --> 00:43:53,940
about your unruly behavior

923
00:43:54,500 --> 00:43:56,060
in my family's

924
00:43:56,380 --> 00:43:58,860
ancestral shrine?

925
00:44:01,540 --> 00:44:02,420
Who hit him?

926
00:44:04,620 --> 00:44:05,300
Xun Chuan.

927
00:44:05,900 --> 00:44:06,580
Yes, Your Highness?

928
00:44:06,860 --> 00:44:07,860
Break his arm.

929
00:44:08,100 --> 00:44:08,620
Yes.

930
00:44:09,300 --> 00:44:10,500
No.

931
00:44:10,700 --> 00:44:11,540
You mustn't do this.

932
00:44:13,660 --> 00:44:15,140
I'll reiterate this.

933
00:44:15,900 --> 00:44:16,740
Pei Wenxuan

934
00:44:17,700 --> 00:44:18,980
is the Prince Consort,

935
00:44:19,140 --> 00:44:20,100
my husband.

936
00:44:20,580 --> 00:44:22,140
If this family doesn't like him,

937
