I'll give him a family.

940
00:44:27,180 --> 00:44:28,460
If you want to keep him,

941
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:30,220
then, from now on,

942
00:44:31,700 --> 00:44:33,380
treat him

943
00:44:35,180 --> 00:44:36,700
like how you will treat me.

944
00:44:42,140 --> 00:44:43,060
As for you, Mrs. Wen...

945
00:44:45,260 --> 00:44:46,580
if you do not know

946
00:44:46,580 --> 00:44:48,460
how to love

947
00:44:49,940 --> 00:44:52,180
or protect your child,

948
00:44:52,940 --> 00:44:55,220
please stay in the family hall
for worshipping the Immortals

949
00:44:55,220 --> 00:44:56,620
