954
00:45:09,020 --> 00:45:09,940
He can allow you to do so.

955
00:45:11,500 --> 00:45:12,700
But I won't.

956
00:45:16,060 --> 00:45:17,100
Am I clear?

957
00:45:34,420 --> 00:45:35,140
Let's go home.

958
00:45:36,980 --> 00:45:37,580
Come on.

959
00:45:38,100 --> 00:45:38,700
